    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Education Classroom Service画一个Git流程图，展示两个功能分支如何并行开发最后合并到主干。主线先有一个初始提交a，然后从main分出feature_1和feature_2两个分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "feature_1",
        "feature_2",
        "commit a"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个分支的显示顺序有要求吗？feature_1在上、feature_2在下可以吗？还有，feature_1需要先切过去做提交f吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature_1 order:0",
        "feature_2 order:2",
        "checkout feature_1",
        "commit f"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，feature_1放上面，order用0和2。流程是：切到feature_1做提交f，然后回到main做提交b，再切回feature_1做提交g。这样main和feature_1就有并行了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "commit b",
        "checkout feature_1",
        "commit g"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主干b和feature_1的g已经画好了。那feature_2这边呢？什么时候切过去？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit b",
        "commit g"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "在feature_1做完g之后，切到feature_2做提交u。然后回到feature_1做h，再去feature_2做v。这样两个分支交替推进，最后都合并回main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout feature_2",
        "commit u",
        "checkout feature_1",
        "commit h",
        "checkout feature_2",
        "commit v"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "交替提交画好了，feature_1有f、g、h，feature_2有u、v。最后合并顺序是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit f",
        "commit g",
        "commit h",
        "commit u",
        "commit v"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先合并feature_1，再合并feature_2，都回到main上。这样整个Education Classroom Service的开发流程就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "merge feature_1",
        "merge feature_2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成了。main上先有a，然后分出两个分支并行开发，中间主干还有b，最后依次合并feature_1和feature_2。整个gitGraph结构符合Education Classroom Service的协作流程。",
